     (Corrects spelling of Illumina in headline)  Illumina Inc. (ILMN)  said that its board of
directors unanimously rejected  Roche Holding AG (ROG) ’s revised offer
to acquire Illumina for $51 per share in cash.  Roche last week raised its bid after earlier offering
$44.50 a share.  To contact the reporter on this story:
